&lt;p&gt;Previous week: (prev:: &lt;a href=&quot;../051---Weekly/2024-W18&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot; data-slug=&quot;051---Weekly/2024-W18&quot;&gt;2024-W18&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;interesting-stuff&quot;&gt;Interesting stuff&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#interesting-stuff&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;log&quot;&gt;Log&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#log&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

051---Weekly/index.richContent:
&lt;p&gt;If &lt;strong&gt;🌴 Jungle&lt;/strong&gt; is an experiment in itself, then &lt;a href=&quot;../051---Weekly/&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;051---Weekly/index&quot;&gt;Weekly&lt;/a&gt; is an experiment inside another experiment. An experiment inception!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’m a big fan of the Obsidian’s &lt;a href=&quot;https://help.obsidian.md/Plugins/Daily+notes&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Daily notes&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; plugin and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/liamcain/obsidian-periodic-notes&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Periodic Notes&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; plugin, which is Daily notes on steroids. I’m using Dailies as a notepad for anything that might come during the day and to give it a &lt;em&gt;small&lt;/em&gt; hope of being reused some day in the future. Dailies are private and &lt;em&gt;very&lt;/em&gt; unstructured.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The plan for the Weekly notes is to make them like Dailies, but with more thought and &lt;a href=&quot;../175---LessWrong/Articles/004---Pain-is-not-the-unit-of-Effort&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;175---LessWrong/Articles/004---Pain-is-not-the-unit-of-Effort&quot;&gt;effort&lt;/a&gt;. Basically I curate everything that I collect in my Dailies and put &lt;em&gt;good enough&lt;/em&gt; stuff in the Weekly note. As such, I’m declaring Weekly notes worthy of being published.&lt;/p&gt;

100---Books/Christopher-Paolini---Eragon.richContent:
&lt;h1 id=&quot;eragon&quot;&gt;Eragon&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#eragon&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
