&lt;p&gt;Obsidian Help: &lt;a href=&quot;https://help.obsidian.md/Editing+and+formatting/Callouts&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;https://help.obsidian.md/Editing+and+formatting/Callouts&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use callouts to include additional content without breaking the flow of your notes.&lt;/p&gt;
