120---Indexing-the-Universe/SPQR.richContent:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPQR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; are the &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Initialism&quot; title=&quot;Initialism&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;initials&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; of a &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latin&quot; title=&quot;Latin&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Latin&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; phrase &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&lt;/strong&gt;enātus &lt;strong&gt;P&lt;/strong&gt;opulus&lt;strong&gt;q&lt;/strong&gt;ue &lt;strong&gt;R&lt;/strong&gt;ōmānus&lt;/em&gt;. It means “The Senate and People of Rome”.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It refers to the &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Government&quot; title=&quot;Government&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;government&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; of the ancient &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roman_Republic&quot; title=&quot;Roman Republic&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Roman Republic&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. It is still used as an official emblem of the modern-day &lt;a href=&quot;../120---Indexing-the-Universe/Municipality&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;120---Indexing-the-Universe/Municipality&quot;&gt;municipality&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rome&quot; title=&quot;Rome&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Rome&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;../011---Public-Assets/Roma-Stemma-2.svg&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; height=&quot;auto&quot; alt=&quot;center&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

