&lt;li&gt;Disturb Undead (from &lt;a href=&quot;../../../../185---TTRPG/050---Pathfinder/001---Characters/001---Beetle/002---Levels#fey-touched-gnome&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;185---TTRPG/050---Pathfinder/001---Characters/001---Beetle/002---Levels&quot;&gt;^fey-touched-gnome&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
