&lt;p&gt;Beetle investigated the curious metalic coin, found on a large skeleton’s body. The coin looks like made out of silver, but it’s really an alloy of unidentified metals. From &lt;a href=&quot;../../../../185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-14---Droga-do-Obalonego-Drzewa#silver-coin&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-14---Droga-do-Obalonego-Drzewa&quot;&gt;^silver-coin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beetle remembers a phrase said by a skeleton; it means &lt;em&gt;something in the lines of&lt;/em&gt;: “Shoot this one!“. From: &lt;a href=&quot;../../../../185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-17---Droga-do-Obalonego-Drzewa-(zamek)#skeleton-shout&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-17---Droga-do-Obalonego-Drzewa-(zamek)&quot;&gt;^skeleton-shout&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I need to select &lt;strong&gt;4 formulas&lt;/strong&gt; from the Basic Crafter’s Book. &lt;a href=&quot;../../../../185---TTRPG/050---Pathfinder/001---Characters/001---Beetle/050---Gear#crafter-book&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;185---TTRPG/050---Pathfinder/001---Characters/001---Beetle/050---Gear&quot;&gt;^crafter-book&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I study the design of sand boats, so I can recreate them if needed in the future. From &lt;a href=&quot;../../../../185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-19---Stary-trakt#sand-boat&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;185---TTRPG/500---Sessions/2024-04-19---Stary-trakt&quot;&gt;^sand-boat&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

