&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hnblogs.substack.com/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;HackerNews blogs newsletter&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — a substack blog aggregating on a daily basis blog entries submitted to&lt;a href=&quot;./tags/HackerNews&quot; class=&quot;tag-link internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;tags/HackerNews&quot;&gt;HackerNews&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://devdocs.io&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;DevDocs&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — combines multiple API documentations in a fast, organized, and searchable interface.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id=&quot;774991&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thepunctuationguide.com/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;The Punctuation Guide&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — The web’s most comprehensive guide to American punctuation. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.goodreads.com/s/article/How-do-I-format-text-into-html-1553870934599&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Goodreads HTML formatting&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — Goodreads supports a set list of html tags that you can use to format your comments, reviews, and stories &amp;#x26; writing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/minimaxir/hacker-news-undocumented/blob/master/README.md&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;A List of Hacker News’s Undocumented Features and Behaviors&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://excalidraw.com/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Excalidraw&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — a virtual collaborative whiteboard tool that lets you easily sketch diagrams that have a hand-drawn feel to them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lesswrong.com/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;LessWrong&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — an online forum and community dedicated to improving human reasoning and decision-making. We seek to hold true beliefs and to be effective at accomplishing our goals. Each day, we aim to be less wrong about the world than the day before.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://obsidian.md/roadmap/&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Obsidian Roadmap&lt;svg class=&quot;external-icon&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt; — list of future&lt;a href=&quot;./tags/Obsidian&quot; class=&quot;tag-link internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;tags/Obsidian&quot;&gt;Obsidian&lt;/a&gt; features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

